      "content": "Yeah, the goal is to make the driving patterns more template-based and easier for the auditors to verify. We're basically stripping away the high-level reasoning and autonomous planning modules since they're too much of a \"black box\" for the current certification standards. Once the update hits, you won't be doing the deep planning anymore, just following the pre-set safety protocols.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
